{
  "stem": "1062.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was one woman there, her name was [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Sodarifca. ?] And she said, all right, children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Come together.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Before you eat, you have to recite the Modeh Ani.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she would have our Modeh Ani, which would last, like an hour and a half, two hours, thinking by the time she's going to be finished with this prayer, with the Modeh Ani, the children will forget that they-- that they are hungry, you know?",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And many times when I think back, you know, those are the things-- those are the things that eats at me, even today.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is something, you know, for the children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They, they were hungry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Certain things, when I think back today, big things, what people here may think is big, doesn't bother me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[CLEARS THROAT] But little things like this, which, you know, I don't know if it's little, but does eats at me even today.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[CLEARS THROAT] Anyway.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[CLEARS THROAT] We were in the ghetto, and then a rumor started to go around.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And one of the rumors was that we are going to be exchanged for German prisoners of war.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Another rumor was that they're going to take us to Madagascar.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know why, but there was a rumor spread in the ghetto that we're going to go to Madagascar.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Another rumor was that we are going to be taken [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], in Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There's a river which is called the Danube.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Transylvania. ?] We will be taken to Transylvania to work the fields over there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "All kinds of rumors.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Now, we were taken to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was on April 15th, when we were on the top, April 15, 1944.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And May 19, 1944, they went ahead and they divided the ghetto into three sections.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
